2008-08-13 17:32  yangtse

	* CHANGES, acinclude.m4, include/curl/curlbuild.h.dist,
	  include/curl/curlbuild.h.in, include/curl/curlrules.h,
	  lib/Makefile.netware, lib/config-symbian.h, lib/config-tpf.h,
