	* src/setup.h: Define CURL_NO_OLDIES to prevent us from getting
	  obsolete stuff defined.

2004-03-02 10:11  bagder

	* src/main.c: CURLOPT_MUTE is obsolete since a long while, we don't
	  need to set it!

